.DS_Store
.dropbox
.dropbox.attr
desktop.ini
Thumbs.db
*.pyc
__pycache__/
# Ignore everything Claude Code writes locally (cache, transcripts,
# settings) EXCEPT project-scoped skills — those describe shared
# workflows that we want versioned alongside the codebase.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**

# Google OAuth client secret — NEVER commit (this repo is public).
# Our code doesn't even use the secret (the backend verifies Google ID
# tokens against Google's public keys), so this file is only a local
# copy of the downloaded credentials. Keep it OUT of git.
client_secret_*.json
*client_secret*.json

# Design references / project docs — not part of the deployed site
*.pdf
sport-icon-options.png
sport-icons-v*.png
pictogrammen/
